                               <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">출력: Large</p>\n                                </div><div class=\"my-2\">\n                                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">입력: 10</p>\n                                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">출력: Small</p>\n                                </div><div class=\"my-2\">\n                                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">입력: 5</p>\n                                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">출력: Small</p>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"mt-4\">\n                            <div id=\"editor4\" class=\"code-editor h-32 border rounded\"></div>\n                        </div>\n                        <button onclick=\"submitAssignment(4, 'implementation_basic')\"\n                            class=\"mt-6 w-full px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-yellow-400 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 hover:from-amber-600 hover:to-yellow-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                            <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"h-5 w-5 mr-2\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"currentColor\">\n                                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\n                            </svg>\n                            코드 제출하기\n                        </button>\n                        <div id=\"result4\" class=\"mt-4 hidden\">\n                            <div class=\"p-4 rounded-lg\"></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md\">\n                    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4\">사용